eu.geclipse.core
Class SolutionRegistry

java.lang.Object
  eu.geclipse.core.SolutionRegistry
Direct Known Subclasses:
DateTimeSolutionRegistry, UISolutionRegistry
public class SolutionRegistry
extends java.lang.Object

This class is the central repository for core related solutions. Whenever no other registry is specified this standard registry is used to query solutions.
